{"tid":725981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翁靜晶鬧執法雙重標準","createTime":"2018-07-02T05:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:04:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc077f7c1b325cb6ebed44a4c9da33c7fc7f505","tid":725981,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180702/20437407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437407&d=cI%2B3Qi0TrAcke%2F3mYbCswP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=11481b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437407&h=6ce317cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180702/20437407</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月02日 <br />\n<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】翁靜晶鬧執法雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180702/large/02ec3p14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180702%2Flarge%2F02ec3p14.jpg&h=956247a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n <br />\n翁靜晶噚日凌晨喺facebook控訴執法部門疑持雙重標準處事，佢話：「政府可以寬容處理唐琳，不追究19萬訴訟費，不拘捕她咬傷入境處人員，卻容不下一個80歲，自食其力養百歲親娘的小販。香港執法雙重標準，已經到了人神共憤的地步&hellip;&hellip;小人物在大世界，根本是沒有公義的。」另外，翁靜晶話上個月有人撞佢屋企大閘，但報咗警亦冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：馮仁昭  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】李力持跟鞏俐做鬼臉<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】陳蕾歐遊大出血"},{"pid":"654979a018cd5c9257fc8b99f445235d690e8d11","tid":725981,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"ad9e9b937fe713a2e1912037733d3ac06a37e007","tid":725981,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"welcome to Hong Kong, China"},{"pid":"46c70b705e5903364ecbe4cf7555d5e426c431d0","tid":725981,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到好似第一日發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caee45a5acbaa3a4670ed034fa4b16e7375e9059","tid":725981,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶應該做律政司司長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b805c76eef26c244466d2a50692dd3cab7b7e37","tid":725981,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"caee45a5acbaa3a4670ed034fa4b16e7375e9059","tid":725981,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶應該做律政司司長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"少林寺班人一樣會照開佢波, 無用"},{"pid":"43bd1113913a5cd9489ede488149b5709700cb0d","tid":725981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，翁靜晶話上個月有人撞佢屋企大閘，但報咗警亦冇辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下係美國?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/a1/4a/7f/a14a7fd6a0a33362bbdb2b89f3666d31--human-rights-country.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2Fa1%2F4a%2F7f%2Fa14a7fd6a0a33362bbdb2b89f3666d31--human-rights-country.jpg&h=acce70d7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}